Azure is a cloud computing platform from Microsoft that provides a wide range of over 200 products and services for building, running, and managing applications and services in the cloud. It offers a flexible and scalable environment for compute, storage, networking, analytics, and AI, hosted in a global network of Microsoft-managed data centers. Businesses can use Azure to optimize operations, improve decision-making, and accelerate developer productivity.  
Tool	Purpose
Azure Cost Management and Billing	Helps monitor, analyze, and control Azure spending with detailed reports and budget alerts.
Azure Pricing Calculator	Estimates the cost of Azure services based on your configuration and usage assumptions.
Azure Advisor	Provides personalized best-practice recommendations for cost optimization, security, reliability, and performance improvements.

